  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA98">
<l>aḻalāṭa vaṅkai civantatō vaṅkai</l>
<l>yaḻakā laḻalcivanta vāṟō - kaḻalāṭap</l>
<l>pēyāṭu kāṉiṟ piṟaṅka vaṉalēntit</l>
<l>tīyāṭu vāyitaṉaic ceppu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When you dance with fire, does [your] palm become red or is the way</l>
<l>that the fire becomes red by the beauty of [your] palm? You who dance</l>
<l>with the fire so that [your] anklets dance, holding the flame so that it glows</l>
<l>in the grove where the demonesses dance, this tell [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
